 With "Reef" Mystic Crock releases his third studio album. He remains true to himself and his style - Ambient, Chillout, Psybient Downtempo... "Reef" starts very quietly and rises gradually to the last song. The album is designed as a mix album to listen to it in one go.
 Mystic Crock gives much observance to sophisticated drone and pad sounds and puts much love in the details like effects and percussions. To perfect the listening experience and to polish the sound to the max he got the legendary AES DANA to master his latest masterpiece.
 Dive into the world of smooth sounds of "Reef" by Mystic Crock
